///////////////////////////////////////////Read Me Wifi Details///////////////////////////
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

This project has the simplest code to get the connected wifi details

To Use this code Please follow the following instruction:

This is a .Net Core Console App Project, so First Simply add a .Net Core Console APP Project 
Add the Shared Dll Reference in the Project
Copy the Code Written in Program.cs to the Program.cs of your Project
Connect You machine to any of the available Wifi
Run the Code and it will show the details of the connected wifi on the console
Currently it will give you Wifi MAC, Name and Status

Happy Coding..!
